title: Rep. McNerney Announces ‘Holiday Cards for the Troops’ Program (Jerry McNerney)
text: ( Source : Jerry McNerney ) Stockton - Today , Congressman Jerry McNerney ( CA-09 ) announced the start of his annual ' Holiday Cards for Our Troops ' program. In previous years, the Congressman's district offices collected more than 8, 000 cards
